value:
Rrrgh... Body...on fire. Curse you,
Izuka! What...did I drink? Urghhh...

Must resist...for the little one...for
my chained brethren... I must fight
for our... Rrrghhh!

That song...I barely can hear it...
and yet...it soothes me. Could it be...

If anything happens to me...take the
little one...leave him in little Sothe's—
I mean Sir Sothe's—care...

When laguz...become Feral Ones...
They lose more than just...rrragh...
their sanity...

Raaagggh! Not enough!
Not nearly enough!

No...must fight these...urges!
They cannot...control me!

I cannot control myself...let alone
a power like this...

I am...Muarim... Raaagh! What is...
happening to me? No, stop! Come
no closer!

Rrrggh...$Nu...$k$pCome no closer...for your own good.
The foul elixir I was forced to drink...
turns laguz like me into Feral Ones.$k$pIt robs us...of our senses. Turns us
into mindless...weapons. It is
repulsive... Rrragh!$k$pI...I'm all right. I must not—will not—
let it control me... Just give me
some space.$k$pI would never...lift a claw...against
you, or the little one... I would...
never...
I am Muarim... I am a laguz!
Do not touch me! You must not come near me now.
Get away! I'll hurt you if you don't…
Agh... My body can't... No, no... Little one... get away!
It's up to you now… Take care of him…
